{"tid":699168,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯指刑期合適：梁天琦唔係羅賓漢只係魚蛋檔","createTime":"2018-06-12T09:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T02:02:50.000Z","uid":83713,"like":7,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63398326a17a54673bc5c155c2c3e209c0f5ff99","tid":699168,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂案本民前前發言人梁天琦暴動罪成被判囚6年，立法會議員何君堯出席電台節目認為刑期合適，認同法官所講參與暴動的人都是咎由自取。公民黨主席梁家傑在同一節目則認為判刑太重，而法官拒絕考慮梁背景及動機是值得商榷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何君堯認為任意妄為和民主自由是兩回事，不能將自己一套加諸別人身上，又指香港人口密集，每次暴動都可引致很大後果，指很多年輕人受誤導走歧途，需發出「理想不是免責金牌」的訊息。何又指梁天琦並非羅賓漢「只不過係魚蛋檔」，指梁保衛小販營業權是多管閒事，又斥梁讀書多更不應以身試法。"},{"pid":"870ba655efa68112a37b9070dc2c3e9e9a5fec6a","tid":699168,"uid":23993,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">殺！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f16a7a7373d956a12140f90177064147902cc18c","tid":699168,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0faa99c1f0417a817838b58e2b552aed910c6cea","tid":699168,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"好撚啜核啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d2953d2db6f0545dd1ac88cbffcc46c4496ef","tid":699168,"uid":17641,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"講真，啲小販本身就唔抵幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e7467c30b8924158d6b455eb6303a1810af9db","tid":699168,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"將佢段說話倒轉黎睇就岩架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2616026a50c623cd6d9f19dfca1aa169f5d4a8b3","tid":699168,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"同話梁天琦尋釁滋事有咩分別<img src=\